img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n返教會啦</blockquote><br />\nbro多謝你提議<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我對基督教冇乜野, 但自己應該就信唔落"},{"pid":"d076117b307e3c31c2c324b7fa337a3f7c784156","tid":85960,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T19:26:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n樣柒<br />\n童顏細粒<br />\n唔知點同人講野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n返教會啦</blockquote><br />\nbro多謝你提議<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我對基督教冇乜野, 但自己應該就信唔落</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實當社交圈子既話係幾好"},{"pid":"157a5cd2dbae55c25a20c4ff30bc2733a1ed104a","tid":85960,"uid":14272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T19:32:12.000Z","msg":"識唔到 同唔想識係兩回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n踏出第一步啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51d5bbef6002f78cfa281c99ed4fff6adabe8c3a","tid":85960,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T02:01:14.000Z","msg":"都係好驚"}]}